      "title": "Kandy Esala Perahera concludes successfully",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sannasa (Scroll of Memorandum) being handed over to President Ranil Wickremesinghe by Temple of the Scared Tooth Relic Chief Custodian Pradeep Nilanga Dela",
        "President Wickremesinghe presents mementos and certificates of appreciation to artistes who participated in the Esala Perahera, keeping in line with the traditions",
        "The traditional ceremony to inform the head of the State on the successful completion of the historic Kandy Esala Perahera was held yesterday at President\u2019s House in Kandy."
      ],
